descriptionHtml:
[center][color=red][size=50px][font=\"Impact\"]Armor Compilation[/font][/size][/color]
[color=dodgerblue]No Requests Will Be Taken At The Moment...Do Not Ask[/color]

Recommended Mods
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17084]Game of Thrones - Followers[/url] by Donker316.

[youtube]_vKS1q0__C8[/youtube]
I want to say thank you to Gopher for this awesome video review...
if you enjoy this video please subscribe to Gophers channel...[url=http://www.youtube.com/user/GophersVids]Here[/url]

[youtube]XRvumFQESy8[/youtube]
3:00---10:53
I want to thank Saiodin for his great work on this video...
Remember to check out Saiodin\'s Channel [url=http://www.youtube.com/show?p=cH_T2FpywzM&tracker=show_av]Skyrim Mod Series[/url] also check out his mod page on the nexus for news...[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13409]Mod Page[/url].

[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/10277-1-1340918590.jpg[/img]
[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/10277-2-1343058562.jpg[/img][img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/10277-1-1343058562.jpg[/img][/center]

[center]=========================================================================================
[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Main Files[/font][/color]
=========================================================================================[/center]

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Compilation[/font][/color]===
-Contents-

>New Slightly Lore Friendly Armors(See List Below)
>New Slightly Lore Friendly Weapons(See List Below)

-Optional Contents-

>Set of Levelist ESPs for having NPCs have the armors(Each Number Represents Chance of Appearing on NPCS.
>Texture and Mesh options

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Weapons List[/font][/color]===
Champion Swords - GreatSword, LongSword
Dragon Bane Axes - BattleAxe, WarAxe
Staff of the Warmage - Mages Staff of Storm Wall
Ice/Icicle - Greatsword/Longsword,Winter is Coming
Longclaw - Longsword,for this night and all nights to come
Sword of the Mountain - Greatsword
-----------------------------
forged and tempered
Advanced Smithing and Daedric for the axes and swords
Steel Smithing for Staff

[center]=========================================================================================
[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Armors[/font][/color]
=========================================================================================[/center]
===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Iron Island[/font][/color]===HEAVY
for the those who may never die out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under steel armor
You must have Ebony Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Winterfell[/font][/color]===HEAVY
for the honorable kings out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under steel armor
You must have Ebony Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Spellweaver[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the cleric or sorceress out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under misc armor
You must have Advanced Armor perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Lannister Guard[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the angry imp out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under steel armor
You must have Advanced Armor perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Arena Mage[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the mage who likes adoring fans out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under leather armor
You must have Advanced Armor perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Armor of the Mountain[/font][/color]===HEAVY
for the 8 foot tall brute out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under steel armor
You must have Ebony Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Warmage[/font][/color]===HEAVY
for the fighting archmage out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under steel armor
You must have Ebony Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Mercenary[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the bounty hunter or gladiator out there...
Now with Arena Standalone...
Can be crafted at a forge under leather armor
You must have Advanced Armor perk
Optional Replacer for Arena Version

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Armor of the White Tree[/font][/color]===LIGHT
AKA Gondor
for the seeker of rings out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under leather armor
You must have Steel Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Champion[/font][/color]===HEAVY
for the great warrior out there...
There are 4 Versions of it   -Blue,Brown,Green,Red-
Can be crafted at a forge under steel armor
You must have Daedric Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]DragonBane[/font][/color]===HEAVY
for the dragon hunter out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under dragon armor
You must have Dragon Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Thane[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the noble swordsman out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under Leather armor
You must have Steel Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]BattleMage[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the warrior mage out there...
There are 4 Versions of it   -White,Black,Imperial,Nord-
Can be crafted at a forge under Steel armor
You must have Elven Smithing perk

===[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Ranger[/font][/color]===LIGHT
for the archer out there...
Can be crafted at a forge under Studded armor
You must have Advanced Armor perk

[center]=========================================================================================
[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Updates[/font][/color]
=========================================================================================[/center]
[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Version 3.6[/font][/color]
-Texture Reworks for Lannister and Winterfell by Bilwit
-Texture Reworks for few armors
-New Levelist Functionality for Better Options

[center]=========================================================================================
[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Other Mods by Me[/font][/color]
=========================================================================================[/center]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2624]Omegared99 - Ancient Nord Female Armor[/url]

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2634]Omegared99 - Female Warrior Normals[/url]

[center]=========================================================================================
[color=dodgerblue][font=\"Impact\"]Credits[/font][/color]
=========================================================================================[/center]
Thank you to Bilwit for your amazing textures for the Lannister and Winterfell Armors

Thank you to CDProjekt for \"The Witcher 2\" and it\'s assets.
